      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in outstanding mint condition \u2014 a genuinely rare find on the used market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with deep, lustrous paint that shows no visible scratches, chips, or blemishes, and all body panels align perfectly with no signs of prior accident damage or repair. The interior is equally impressive, presenting like new with clean, unmarked upholstery, fully functional controls, and no unpleasant odors. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, all mechanical systems are in excellent working order, and the tires retain strong tread depth. This is a well-maintained vehicle that has clearly been cared for with great attention, and it represents a genuine opportunity to acquire a used car that feels and performs like a much newer model.",
